1
00:01:31,480 --> 00:01:32,640
In that moment,

2
00:01:33,440 --> 00:01:36,039
you were the only person on my mind.

3
00:01:50,800 --> 00:01:52,200
Whose clothes are you wearing?

4
00:01:52,200 --> 00:01:53,000
Yours.

5
00:01:54,200 --> 00:01:55,729
Who let you wear my clothes?

6
00:01:56,560 --> 00:01:58,160
My dress got wet.

7
00:01:58,479 --> 00:02:00,080
It's uncomfortable to wear.

8
00:02:01,320 --> 00:02:02,780
It's thundering outside.

9
00:02:03,040 --> 00:02:05,800
Can I stay here tonight?

10
00:02:09,240 --> 00:02:10,500
Let me tell you, Su Xia.

11
00:02:10,800 --> 00:02:13,330
Don't push your luck
just because I saved you.

12
00:02:13,920 --> 00:02:14,560
Get out.

13
00:02:23,200 --> 00:02:23,840
Leave.

14
00:02:24,200 --> 00:02:26,280
But when I felt sick before,

15
00:02:26,400 --> 00:02:28,120
you would lull me to sleep.

16
00:02:35,280 --> 00:02:36,410
Go find Xiao Qi then.

17
00:02:40,120 --> 00:02:40,920
Are you...

18
00:02:42,600 --> 00:02:43,520
jealous?

19
00:02:47,240 --> 00:02:49,560
Don't worry. I won't do anything to you.

20
00:02:49,760 --> 00:02:51,360
I'm really not feeling well.

21
00:02:51,800 --> 00:02:53,200
I think I have a fever.

22
00:02:54,320 --> 00:02:55,840
If you really don't believe me,

23
00:02:55,840 --> 00:02:56,960
you can tie me up.

24
00:03:35,480 --> 00:03:36,480
Thanks, Brother.

25
00:03:40,000 --> 00:03:41,400
Don't just look at me.

26
00:03:42,000 --> 00:03:43,200
You should sleep too.

27
00:03:55,320 --> 00:03:57,480
Good night, Brother.

28
00:04:12,440 --> 00:04:13,970
Don't make me throw you out!

29
00:04:24,680 --> 00:04:25,400
Brother.

30
00:05:27,200 --> 00:05:27,920
Brother.

31
00:05:41,360 --> 00:05:42,120
Brother.

32
00:06:57,480 --> 00:06:58,120
Brother.

33
00:06:58,240 --> 00:06:58,920
Shut up.

34
00:07:02,120 --> 00:07:02,880
Get out.

35
00:07:09,480 --> 00:07:10,240
Xia.

36
00:07:11,880 --> 00:07:12,520
Morning.

37
00:07:19,040 --> 00:07:21,100
Did you enjoy the banquet last night?

38
00:07:25,040 --> 00:07:26,000
It's so bitter.

39
00:07:26,000 --> 00:07:28,060
You didn't add sugar? It's terrible.

40
00:07:29,120 --> 00:07:30,520
Fun or not,

41
00:07:30,720 --> 00:07:34,580
it's still better than listening to
the old man's financial reports.

42
00:07:39,240 --> 00:07:40,200
You've been

43
00:07:41,280 --> 00:07:43,280
getting very close to Lu Fan lately.

44
00:07:45,800 --> 00:07:46,800
Are you jealous?

45
00:07:47,680 --> 00:07:48,920
Don't worry.

46
00:07:49,480 --> 00:07:50,680
He is my brother,

47
00:07:51,159 --> 00:07:52,560
and I am his sister.

48
00:07:54,960 --> 00:07:55,880
That's good.

49
00:07:56,680 --> 00:07:58,340
Remember, he's your brother.

50
00:07:58,440 --> 00:07:59,600
And will always be.

51
00:08:00,640 --> 00:08:01,440
Of course.

52
00:08:01,880 --> 00:08:03,240
I also remember

53
00:08:03,480 --> 00:08:05,200
all the sacrifices you made for me,

54
00:08:05,200 --> 00:08:07,280
including marrying into the Lu family

55
00:08:07,280 --> 00:08:10,280
and working so hard
to take care of my brother-in-law.

56
00:08:14,440 --> 00:08:16,520
Brother, wait for me.

57
00:08:17,880 --> 00:08:19,200
Brother, wait for me.

58
00:08:35,280 --> 00:08:37,010
Mr. Xiao, what brings you here?

59
00:08:38,120 --> 00:08:39,360
You didn't answer my call.

60
00:08:39,360 --> 00:08:40,159
I was worried about your injury,

61
00:08:40,159 --> 00:08:41,490
so I came to check on you.

62
00:08:42,440 --> 00:08:44,500
I hope I'm not disturbing you, Mr. Lu.

63
00:08:50,560 --> 00:08:52,880
Fan, I'm also here to visit Su Xia.

64
00:08:53,480 --> 00:08:55,560
After what happened last night,

65
00:08:55,680 --> 00:08:57,240
I feel really bad.

66
00:08:58,360 --> 00:08:59,890
It's none of your business.

67
00:09:01,080 --> 00:09:02,040
Have you eaten?

68
00:09:02,400 --> 00:09:03,440
Not yet.

69
00:09:03,440 --> 00:09:05,100
Let's go get something to eat.

70
00:09:14,360 --> 00:09:15,400
I'm hungry too.

71
00:09:15,880 --> 00:09:17,000
I'll just eat here.

72
00:09:20,560 --> 00:09:21,680
I really didn't expect

73
00:09:21,680 --> 00:09:24,280
we'd have
such a distinguished visitor today.

74
00:09:24,960 --> 00:09:26,640
Come on, let's raise our glasses together

75
00:09:26,640 --> 00:09:27,770
to welcome Mr. Xiao.

76
00:09:33,880 --> 00:09:35,640
Su Xia, I'm really sorry.

77
00:09:36,200 --> 00:09:38,530
I didn't expect
Wu Qing to still be the same

78
00:09:38,760 --> 00:09:40,360
and actually do such a thing.

79
00:09:42,040 --> 00:09:43,120
We are one.

80
00:09:44,200 --> 00:09:45,200
Miss Jian Xi,

81
00:09:45,360 --> 00:09:46,960
you are really too polite.

82
00:09:48,200 --> 00:09:49,400
Actually, this time,

83
00:09:49,480 --> 00:09:51,040
I must also thank you very much

84
00:09:51,040 --> 00:09:53,300
for the banquet held by your Jian family.

85
00:09:53,680 --> 00:09:54,760
It allowed Xia

86
00:09:56,120 --> 00:09:58,180
to have the honor of meeting Mr. Xiao.

87
00:10:00,200 --> 00:10:02,680
Then I hope, Mr. Xiao and Su Xia,

88
00:10:02,760 --> 00:10:04,820
you can have a happy ending together.

89
00:10:05,120 --> 00:10:05,880
Thank you.

90
00:10:06,840 --> 00:10:07,880
Thank you, Xi.

91
00:10:08,360 --> 00:10:11,000
I also hope
the two of you get married soon.

92
00:10:27,320 --> 00:10:28,120
By the way,

93
00:10:28,400 --> 00:10:30,040
Wu Qing asked me for a favor.

94
00:10:30,120 --> 00:10:32,850
She wants to apologize
to the Lu family in person.

95
00:10:34,360 --> 00:10:35,200
Miss Jian.

96
00:10:37,320 --> 00:10:38,240
Has that Wu person

97
00:10:38,240 --> 00:10:40,840
got the person she's apologizing to
all wrong?

98
00:10:42,400 --> 00:10:46,080
Wu Qing really should apologize to Su Xia.

99
00:10:47,880 --> 00:10:49,280
When a person can even

100
00:10:49,280 --> 00:10:50,920
get the apology target wrong,

101
00:10:50,920 --> 00:10:51,680
her apology

102
00:10:51,680 --> 00:10:53,440
isn't even worth hearing.

103
00:10:56,120 --> 00:10:58,180
Even if the Lu family wants to hear it,

104
00:10:59,720 --> 00:11:01,320
my Xiao family won't.

105
00:11:03,720 --> 00:11:05,580
Su Xia is a member of the Lu family.

106
00:11:05,600 --> 00:11:07,000
We will handle this matter.

107
00:11:07,000 --> 00:11:08,800
You don't need to worry about it.

108
00:11:10,400 --> 00:11:11,360
Are you so sure

109
00:11:11,360 --> 00:11:13,480
that Su Xia
won't be a member of the Xiao family?

110
00:11:13,480 --> 00:11:14,560
Never.

111
00:11:15,840 --> 00:11:16,920
So confident?

112
00:11:17,000 --> 00:11:18,080
I have always been confident.

113
00:11:18,080 --> 00:11:19,040
Let's wait and see.

114
00:11:19,040 --> 00:11:19,720
Let's see.

115
00:11:19,720 --> 00:11:20,520
Lu Fan.

116
00:11:21,960 --> 00:11:22,920
You have no manners.

117
00:11:22,920 --> 00:11:25,520
Mr. Xiao is our distinguished guest.

118
00:11:27,400 --> 00:11:29,200
He is your distinguished guest,

119
00:11:29,280 --> 00:11:30,240
not ours.

120
00:11:36,520 --> 00:11:37,920
I've got company business to take care of.

121
00:11:37,920 --> 00:11:38,920
I'll leave first.

122
00:11:40,800 --> 00:11:42,460
I'll have the driver send you.

123
00:11:43,480 --> 00:11:44,320
Lu Fan.

124
00:11:44,600 --> 00:11:45,400
Lu Fan!
